I remember when MTF,(Much Too FAst), wasn't always Quick Thinking:<br><br>
Once on Hill 65 when both MTF and SW arrived in their choppers overhead at the same time. <br><br>
It was just in time for the annual USO show and only one small parking spot for a lone chopper remained on the hill.<br><br>
The Flight controler said, &quot;Mustang Two Four&quot;, &quot;Silent Warrior&quot;, you both arrived at the same time. <br>
We only have room for one more chopper, which one of you wants to come in?&quot;<br><br>
MTF immediately heard, &quot;Go ahead, Silent Warrior, You can go!&quot; and knew he had been had.<br><br>

